  "title": "Maintenance Technician",
  "description": "<p>🌟 <strong>We’re Hiring! | Maintenance Technician</strong></p>\n<p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong>Tuas, Singapore<br>\n 💼 <strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-Time<br>\n 💰 <strong>Salary:</strong>$2,500 – $4,000/month<br>\n 🕒 <strong>Working Hours:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Monday to Friday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM</li>\n  <li>Saturday: 8:30 AM – 12:30 PM<br>\n 🚍 <strong>Transport:</strong> Company-provided transport from Joo Koon MRT<br>\n 🚀 <strong>Availability:</strong> Immediate</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>About the Role</strong></p>\n<p>We are seeking a dedicated <strong>Maintenance Technician</strong> to join our team in Tuas. The ideal candidate should have hands-on experience in maintaining and repairing food processing machinery, refrigeration systems, and related equipment.</p>\n<p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform maintenance, troubleshooting, and repair of food processing      machines, production equipment, coolers, freezers, chillers, and related      systems.</li>\n  <li>Conduct preventive maintenance to ensure equipment reliability and      minimize downtime.</li>\n  <li>Perform electrical and mechanical repair works.</li>\n  <li>Support the installation, testing, and commissioning of new      machines or systems.</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate maintenance and service records.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with safety, hygiene, and operational standards      in the production area.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of relevant experience in food machinery,      refrigeration, or industrial equipment maintenance.</li>\n  <li>Education: NITEC / Higher NITEC / Diploma (ITE or Polytechnic,      Singapore).</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of electrical and mechanical systems, safety standards,      and hazard protocols.</li>\n  <li>Responsible, proactive, and able to work independently in a      fast-paced environment.</li>\n</ul>",
